As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 73 people, 42 households, and 35 families residing in the town.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2020: Belleair Shore town, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Belleair+Shore+town;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

As of the [[2010 United States census]], there were 109 people, 29 households, and 21 families residing in the town.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2010: Belleair Shore town, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Belleair+Shore+town;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2010.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

